text: I know you said you were hesitant to return to RE2, but you might still like it. Playing a 2nd Run adds new weapons, changes your ammo economy, and has the real final boss you don't fight on the 1st Run. There were also three DLCs that add content as well as the 4th Survivor minigame that expects you to have a high skill level to complete it. I'd really like to watch you play 4th Survivor in particular. It's widely considered the "filter" that separates the skilled players from the bad players.
